LogJammin 0.1

Depends on the following libraries:
    tokyocabinet
    tokyodystopia
    lua
    libedit (optional)
    curl
    crypto
    expact

Configure using:
    ./waf configure

    options
        --dbdir=["/var/db/logjam"]

Build using:
    ./waf build


Storage configuration parameters:
    main - main database config.
    main/file - filename to load as the main database file.
    main/mode/[0-9]+ - mode to open the database file (not yet implemented).
            (options: create read write)
    main/compare - key type for tree db (not yet implemented).
            (options: int64 lex decimal ljkey / defaults int64)
    main/type - type of database to use (not yet implemented).
            (options: tree hash / default tree)
    index - configuration entries for the different index types.
    index/tree - B+Tree Index configuration -- supports ranges.
    index/hash - Hash index configuration (not yet implemented).
    index/text - Text index.
    index/tag - Word or phrase index, no substrings.

All indicies are configured the same way at the moment. The configuration
for an index goes in the configuration structure at the following key:
    index/<type>/<unique_id>

example
    index/tree/role_name

An index is configured with the following parameters:
    file - filename to load as the main database file.
    mode/[0-9]+ - mode to open the database file (not yet implemented).
            (options: create read write)
    compare - key type for tree db (not yet implemented).
            (options: int64 lex decimal ljkey / defaults int64)
    type - type of database to use (not yet implemented, might go away).
            (options: tree hash / default tree)
    field - path into the document to find the value to index.

example document:
{
  "main":{
    "compare":"int64",
    "file":"db_role.tcb",
    "mode":{
      "0":"READER",
      "1":"WRITER",
      "2":"CREATE"
    },
    "type":"tree"
  },
  "index":{
    "text":{
      "name":{
        "compare":"lex",
        "field":"name",
        "file":"text_name.tdq",
        "mode":{
          "0":"READER",
          "1":"WRITER",
          "2":"CREATE"
        }
      }
    },
    "tree":{
      "name":{
        "compare":"lex",
        "field":"name",
        "file":"tree_name.tcb",
        "mode":{
          "0":"READER",
          "1":"WRITER",
          "2":"CREATE"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
